<plot>The pop singer Sonja has to perform an emergency landing with her two-seater in the mountains of Tirol. There she discovers the yodeling lumberjack Toni. She persuades him to come with her into town and to start a career in the music business. Toni's spouse Maria stays behind, worried, and with a broken heart. Will he ever come back?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?242264</url></doc>
